    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2009-04-27</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2009-05-18T18:27:23Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Correspondence With Our Heroes Act - Directs the Secretary of Defense to provide for a one-year program under which postal benefit vouchers are provided for the benefit of members of the Armed Forces on active duty in Iraq or Afghanistan, or hospitalized at a military facility as a result of a disease or injury incurred as a result of such service. Entitles voucher users to make free mailings to such individuals. Limits vouchers to one per month.</p> <p>Requires the Department of Defense (DOD) to transfer to the Postal Service an amount representing the amount of the vouchers used.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
